            "title": "業務重組｜索尼影視啟動重組 擬裁減數百人 強調非為節省成本",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"376\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ruEj0AlxV6XdVFyRreiLNQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUzOQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/bossmind_356/c40953ffe11e3fd15d847b119e47c93a\" width=\"670\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">路透引述消息報道，索尼影視娛樂（Sony Pictures Entertainment）正啟動業務重組，計劃向全球電影、電視和企業部門開刀，預計將在數月內裁員數百人。消息人士透露，是次裁員並非為了節省成本，而是有針對性且具策略性的，以配合其長期增長策略。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據索尼影視娛樂行政總裁Ravi Ahuja向員工發出的內部信，表示裁員是艱難的決定，「我們正在讓組織架構順應業務未來的發展方向，而非固守過往模式，這需要調整公司架構佈局與投資方向」，同時又指將加強對關乎未來發展核心領域的投入與關注。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-719221a6-22d5-32de-8bd2-b4972698eb7a-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Ahuja雖未披露具體裁員數字與部門分配比例，但消息人士指，此次裁員主要集中在電影、電視以及公司職能部門。Ahuja續指，儘管整個行業受到衝擊，但索尼仍處於有利地位，公司擁有強大的獨立電影和電視工作室，能廣泛與多個平台合作，而非依賴單一內部串流服務。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">另外，索尼對核心領域的投入加大，被業界解讀為有意向版權IP營運、串流平台Crunchyroll及遊戲改編內容等高潛力板塊傾斜資源。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">索尼最新財務數據顯示，公司影視娛樂板塊正遭遇顯著成長壓力。根據索尼集團2026財年第三季財報，其經營利潤5,150億日元，年增22%；純利3,773億日元，年增11%。這當中影視業務收入年減11%，營利較去年同期下降9%。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%A5%AD%E5%8B%99%E9%87%8D%E7%B5%84-%E7%B4%A2%E5%B0%BC%E5%BD%B1%E8%A6%96%E5%95%9F%E5%8B%95%E9%87%8D%E7%B5%84-%E6%93%AC%E8%A3%81%E6%B8%9B%E6%95%B8%E7%99%BE%E4%BA%BA-%E5%BC%B7%E8%AA%BF%E9%9D%9E%E7%82%BA%E7%AF%80%E7%9C%81%E6%88%90%E6%9C%AC-075546687.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-08 16:00:51",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "市區半新樓2房連平台6球推拍 樓價7年蒸發44% 貶值510萬元",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">樓市交投轉旺，拍賣場又見低價筍盤。樓齡7年的大角咀<a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"利奧坊‧凱岸\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:利奧坊‧凱岸;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/47PwvK6\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">利奧坊‧凱岸</a>一個2房連平台特色戶，屬市區罕有放盤，銀主將於下周二（4月14日）假環亞物業拍賣行以660萬元推拍，料將吸引用家及投資者爭購。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"720\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/5BKRDq9gh_hewtIHADNSAg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyMA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/d210ca553c521360c9931e81b635cb8b\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">更多消息：</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"旺角劏舖搶高6倍至70萬沽 每月收租4,000元 業主持貨14年仍蝕77%\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:旺角劏舖搶高6倍至70萬沽 每月收租4,000元 業主持貨14年仍蝕77%;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4twdJzH\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">旺角劏舖搶高6倍至70萬沽 每月收租4,000元 業主持貨14年仍蝕77%</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"德福五屍命案單位流拍 「凶宅大王」未舉手已敗陣：「出師未捷身未死」 「鬼王」潘紹聰稱單位「安全、舒服、有人氣」\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:德福五屍命案單位流拍 「凶宅大王」未舉手已敗陣：「出師未捷身未死」 「鬼王」潘紹聰稱單位「安全、舒服、有人氣」;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/47P77nJ\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">德福五屍命案單位流拍 「凶宅大王」未舉手已敗陣：「出師未捷身未死」 「鬼王」潘紹聰稱單位「安全、舒服、有人氣」</a></p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"720\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/JYrOOwuz8mMgkJrHcw1Y.g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyMA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/fba971123ecb94fa9a81d814aeaadc6c\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">上述單位為利奧坊‧凱岸2座低層連平台單位，實用面積379平方呎，採2房間隔，連144平方呎平台，將於下周二以660萬元開拍，折合呎價僅約17,414元。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-7a86a1b9-f3e9-3c6c-905f-011ce42d0ec6-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"720\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/0B7Mvy2OcvXPmckjvtPnlQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyMA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/0a2c27c005becbdfbf6559398746a478\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">從放盤相可見，單位內籠新淨，採開放式廚房，玄關及客廳訂造大型儲物櫃。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"720\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/J7EWzbZ3RZeBJQvxTqFgKw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyMA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/fffba15c2246769a983fc57e08ea3b17\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">靠近客廳的細房設有閣樓及衣櫃，主人房訂造地台床及置物架。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"720\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/_9vCxMqjSBmLjWJk729ZdQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyMA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/1b85f775d781e7fa87766bb1722c764b\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">衛生間有窗可通風。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"720\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Un..bJ5sx3K0Ev4ixRi2qw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyMA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/977bd4c818ac2470647bb60d940b14ba\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">單位將於明日（4月9日）開放參觀。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"720\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/7GN5fGSlpOq5hxVTqknS1A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyMA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/f9df5575a97cb85a668abb605191cd0c\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據悉，原業主於2019年11月以1,170.05萬元購入單位，其後斷供淪為銀主盤，早前曾3度流拍，今次開價與之前3次相若，較約7年前買入價低510.05萬元或44%，較銀行估價739萬元亦低約11%。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"720\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/CLjHG0OhMQw9_F0YE0cRxw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyMA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/d0477b4475ca9ec6230a714ae5dffec6\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據28Hse網站資料，利奧坊‧凱岸近期平均成交呎價約18,774 元，較上述單位開拍呎價高1,360元或7.8%。屋苑目前共<a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"17個放盤\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:17個放盤;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4ttL7qJ\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">17個放盤</a>，涵蓋開放式至1房，叫價由370萬元至551萬元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">延伸閱讀: <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"大角咀\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:大角咀;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/大角咀-27379\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">大角咀</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"旺角\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:旺角;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/旺角-27383\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">旺角</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">延伸閱讀:</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">* <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"新聞連結\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:新聞連結;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/news/%E5%B8%82%E5%8D%80%E5%8D%8A%E6%96%B0%E6%A8%932%E6%88%BF%E9%80%A3%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B06%E7%90%83%E6%8E%A8%E6%8B%8D-%E6%A8%93%E5%83%B97%E5%B9%B4%E8%92%B8%E7%99%BC44-%E8%B2%B6%E5%80%BC510%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83-75425\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">新聞連結</a>。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">* <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"28Hse App\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:28Hse App;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/appdownload\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">28Hse App</a>。</p></div>",
